title: Google\Cloud\Logging\V2\LogView
name: LogView
description:
Describes a view over log entries in a bucket.

Generated from protobuf message google.logging.v2.LogView

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.name
params.description: The resource name of the view. For example: projects/my-project/locations/global/buckets/my-bucket/views/my-view

params.name: data.create_time
params.description: Output only. The creation timestamp of the view.

params.name: data.update_time
params.description: Output only. The last update timestamp of the view.

params.name: data.filter
params.description: Filter that restricts which log entries in a bucket are visible in this view. Filters are restricted to be a logical AND of ==/!= of any of the following: - originating project/folder/organization/billing account. - resource type - log id For example: SOURCE("projects/myproject") AND resource.type = "gce_instance" AND LOG_ID("stdout")

Filter that restricts which log entries in a bucket are visible in this view.

Filters are restricted to be a logical AND of ==/!= of any of the following:

  • originating project/folder/organization/billing account.
  • resource type
  • log id For example: SOURCE("projects/myproject") AND resource.type = "gce_instance" AND LOG_ID("stdout")
